echosmart-gateway (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * C++ binaries: echosmart-gateway-bin, echosmart-sysinfo, echosmart-sensor-read.
  * Systemd service for automatic startup.
  * Setup wizard for first-run configuration.
  * Supports DS18B20, DHT22, BH1750, soil moisture and MH-Z19C sensors.

 -- EchoSmart Team <soporte@echosmart.io>  Sat, 29 Mar 2026 08:00:00 +0000
